Habakkuk 2-9 <pb/><t><f>ⓤ</f> “Woe to him who gets evil gain for his house, </t><t><f>ⓥ</f>to <f>ⓦ</f>set his nest on high, </t><t>to be safe from the reach of harm!</t>
