Habakkuk 2-11 <t>For <f>ⓨ</f>the stone will cry out from the wall, </t><t>and the beam from the woodwork respond. </t>
Habakkuk 2-12 <pb/><t><f>ⓩ</f> “Woe to him <f>ⓐ</f>who builds a town with blood </t><t>and founds a city on iniquity!</t>
